  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the Capacities of Shelters and Governmental Migratory Facilities in the Southern Border of Mexico</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to strengthen the capacities of faith based and civil society shelters and improve the access to decent accommodation in Mexico. The general objective is to support the government of Mexico, civil society and faith-based actors who provide attention to migrants from El Salvador, Guatemala, Honduras and Nicaragua to access accommodation and dignified basic services in government installations and in civil society organizations shelters in an environment that promotes and respects human rights.</narrative>
  </description>
